      "date": "2011-12-18 03:28:20.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on el5/x86_64, el6/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/52e9413a-2928-11e1-b25e-5254004bbbd3).  Ran 1 tests.  1 tests failed: node-provisioning-1.",
