      },
      "date": "2011-12-18 05:34:42.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nOn FC13 any file not ending in .conf gets a warning printed that a future version of modprobe will ignore it. \n\nI don't think we currently create this file ourselves in an RPM, but it makes sense to change the documentation to refer to lustre.conf so that new systems start to use this.",
